---
title  : Promenade
summary: Software Production Mangement
contact: Trans <transfire@gmail.com>

description:
  Promenade is an advanced lifecycle build system.
  With Promenade, build tasks are user defined service
  instances tied to stops along a track. Whenever the
  promenade console command is run, a track is followed
  from beginning to designated destination.

requires:
  - redtools
  - facets
  - pom
  - qed (test)

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/promenade
  code: http://github.com/rubyworks/promenade
  mail: http://groups.google.com/rubyworks-mailinglist

repositories:
  public: http://github.com/proutils/promenade.git

